{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And how I didn't kill myself, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I run into that woods, or crawled into that woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- at that time, I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he kept an eye on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from that camp-- from in those woods, I saw a bottle with white fluid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a lot of medicines that people took out from the-- from lager one, because there were doctors, many doctors, especially Lithuanian Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That were in-- this was called the camp where the Lithuanian Jews were kept.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were medication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know where I got it from or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a white bottle with white stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's going to sound very stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I opened that bottle, and I drank it, the whole bottle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is how thirsty I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is how I didn't care what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told it to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, how could you do it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to kill your-- kill your-- Do you know what it was?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could have been-- I mean, the white stuff, what is it called?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Milk of magnesia, it could have been anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't know at that time what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, when my father came off that train, he had-- his hand was cut by a can of food, you know, the military cans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had this can-- he had this can constantly on the train with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know where he got it from and what was even inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because nothing at that time mattered to me anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, somebody wanted to pull it out from his hand, so they cut his left hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the time we came to Dachau, he had already gangrene.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
